CustomField.formula: RIGHT( Street, LEN(Street) - MIN( IF(FIND("0", Street) = 0, 999, FIND("0", Street)), IF(FIND("1", Street) = 0, 999, FIND("1", Street)), IF(FIND("2", Street) = 0, 999, FIND("2", Street)), IF(FIND("3", Street) = 0, 999, FIND("3", Street)), IF(FIND("4", Street) = 0, 999, FIND("4", Street)), IF(FIND("5", Street) = 0, 999, FIND("5", Street)), IF(FIND("6", Street) = 0, 999, FIND("6", Street)), IF(FIND("7", Street) = 0, 999, FIND("7", Street)), IF(FIND("8", Street) = 0, 999, FIND("8", Street)), IF(FIND("9", Street) = 0, 999, FIND("9", Street)) ) + 1 )
CustomField.label: Hausnummer
